Not free from boding thoughts, awhile The shepherd stood ; then makes his way O'er rocks and stones, following the dog As quickly as he may ;

N or far had gone before he found

The appalled discoverer with a sigh Looks round to learn the history.

From those abrupt and perilous rocks The man had fallen, that place of fear!
